Census 2000 PHC-T-28.  Employment Status of the Population in Households for the United States, States, Counties, Places, and for Puerto Rico:  2000
Table 1.  Employment Status of the Population 16 Years Old and Over in Households for the United States, States, Counties, and for Puerto Rico: 2000
Source:  U.S. Census Bureau, Census 2000, special tabulation.

Note:  This houshold-only county file was reposted on November 4, 2003, to correct errors in the estimates for several counties in Puerto Rico.  An error in the county codes for Puerto Rico caused the previous version's estimates to be switched among these municipios: Anasco, Arecibo, Arroyo, Guanica, Guayama, Guayanilla, Guaynabo, and Gurabo.  The estimates have been corrected in this new version.
[Data based on a sample.  For information on confidentiality protection, sampling error, nonsampling error, and definitions, see, http://www.census.gov/prod/cen2000/doc/sf3.pdf]
